### ============================================
### Ticket Service API (Port 8081)
### ============================================
### 항공권 발급 및 관리


### ------------------------------------------
### 항공권 발급
### ------------------------------------------

### 새 항공권 발급
POST http://localhost:8081/v1/tickets
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reservationId": "RES-001",
  "flightId": "KE001",
  "passengerName": "Kim Minsu",
  "seatNumber": "23A",
  "seatClass": "ECONOMY",
  "departureTime": "2024-12-25T10:00:00",
  "arrivalTime": "2024-12-25T11:10:00"
}

###

### 항공권 조회
GET http://localhost:8081/v1/tickets/TKT-001
Accept: application/json


### ------------------------------------------
### 항공권 취소
### ------------------------------------------

### 항공권 취소
POST http://localhost:8081/v1/tickets/TKT-001/cancel
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Flight cancelled",
  "refundTicket": true
}


### ------------------------------------------
### 항공권 검증
### ------------------------------------------

### 항공권 유효성 검증
POST http://localhost:8081/v1/tickets/TKT-001/validate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "passengerName": "Kim Minsu",
  "flightId": "KE001"
}
